<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad">

<body>

<metal:leftportlets fill-slot="portlets_one">
</metal:leftportlets>

<metal:rightportlets fill-slot="portlets_two">
</metal:rightportlets>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">

  <div metal:use-macro="context/@@launchpad_addform/addform">

    <div metal:fill-slot="extra_info" class="documentDescription">
      Please describe the bounty you are registering below. You will be the
      "creator" of this bounty, listed in perpetuity, so please take care to
      get the details correct. Most important is to include contact details
      for the relevant person issuing the bounty, in the description of the
      bounty itself.
    </div>

  </div>

  <div>
    Once again, please double-check your information above before submitting
    the form. In particular, make sure you have given contact details for
    the person coordinating the bounty, and have the amount in USD correct.
    Thank you!
  </div>

</div>
    
</body>
</html>

